Setup
=====
ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C "rantaoca@gmail.com"
cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
https://github.com/settings/ssh/new

sudo apt-get install git
git clone git@github.com:rantaoca/nix-profile.git ~/.ranconf
~/.ranconf/setup.sh

# Install vim plugins by running :PlugInstall in a vim session.


Remap escape/caps
=================
On Ubuntu >18.04:
$ gnome-tweaks
Keyboard & Mouse > Additional Layout Options > Caps Lock Behavior


Ignore case for tab autocomplete
================================
echo 'set completion-ignore-case On' >> /etc/inputrc



